room_title: Escape room "The Haunted Prison" by Lockology Columbus in Columbus
review: The Haunted Prison was a challenging and fun experience.  The room is dim and make you feel like you are really in an old run down prison.  We were with another Group who we hadn't met before and they were awesome to have with us!

room_title: Escape room "The Haunted Prison" by Lockology Columbus in Columbus
review: Was really unimpressed by this room. Only 2 of the puzzles were challenging. The rest were locks. My group finished the room in 32 minutes and we were really disappointed in the ease. Not worth the cost.

room_title: Escape room "The Haunted Prison" by Lockology Columbus in Columbus
review: This room has enough of a spooky atmosphere to make you feel a bit nervouse about what is going to startle you next.  Fun and challenging!!!
